OL,3,CAncient Monument bridge re-opens after
OL,4,Croad accident caused 'extensive damage'
OL,6,FAn historic bridge has now re-opened
OL,7,Fto traffic, following an early morning
OL,8,Froad accident which caused 'extensive
OL,9,Fdamage'.
OL,11,FAt around 1am on Wednesday 17 June, a
OL,12,Fcrash damaged 10 metres of the parapet
OL,13,Fwall of Kendal's Nether Bridge.
OL,15,FCouncil highway teams attended the
OL,16,Fscene and closed the road to traffic,
OL,17,Fbut following safety inspections the
OL,18,Fbridge has now been re-opened to
OL,19,Fvehicles.
