PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F322A1781696868
OL,3,CAncient Monument bridge re-opens after
OL,4,Croad accident caused 'extensive damage'
OL,6,FConcrete barriers have been installed
OL,7,Falongside the damaged wall, but the
OL,8,Ffootway remains closed.
OL,10,FNether Bridge is a 'Scheduled Ancient
OL,11,FMonument,' which recognises the
OL,12,Fbridge's status as a nationally
OL,13,Fimportant or historic building.
OL,15,FWestmorland and Furness council says
OL,16,Fit will now recover what it can of the
OL,17,Fheritage stonework that was knocked
OL,18,Finto the river during the accident,
OL,19,Fwith the intention of reusing this in
OL,20,Frepair works.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/3
