PN,32203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F322A1781696868
OL,3,CAncient Monument bridge re-opens after
OL,4,Croad accident caused 'extensive damage'
OL,6,FBefore an underwater contractor can go
OL,7,Finto the river to recover this
OL,8,Fmasonry, however, Habitat Regulations
OL,9,FAssessment surveys and reports from
OL,10,FNatural England will be required.
OL,12,FThe council said that while it cannot
OL,13,Fyet give a firm timeline, "this will
OL,14,Finevitably (take) a number of months".
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
